### Library Management System - Books API
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000/api

### ========================================
### CADASTRAR LIVROS
### ========================================

### Cadastrar Livro Clássico
POST http://localhost:3000/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "O Senhor dos Anéis",
  "year": 1954,
  "publisher": "Allen & Unwin"
}

### Cadastrar Livro Brasileiro
POST http://localhost:3000/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dom Casmurro",
  "year": 1899,
  "publisher": "Livraria Garnier"
}

### Cadastrar Livro Moderno
POST http://localhost:3000/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "1984",
  "year": 1949,
  "publisher": "Secker & Warburg"
}

### ========================================
### PESQUISAR LIVROS
### ========================================

### Pesquisar por "senhor"
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books/search?q=senhor

### Pesquisar por "dom"
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books/search?q=dom

### Pesquisar por "1984"
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books/search?q=1984

### Pesquisar por "anéis"
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books/search?q=anéis

### Pesquisar vazia (deve retornar todos)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books/search?q=

